  "prompt": "Where is a reliable mobile repair shop to get my phone screen replaced in Kolkata?",
  "response": "When looking for a reliable mobile repair shop to get your phone screen replaced in Kolkata, you have several options to consider. The following are some reputed repair shops and service centers known for their quality service:\n\n1. **Cell Care**:\n   - Location: 92/2, Ekdalia Rd, Ballygunge Place, Kolkata\n   - Known for good customer service and prompt repairs.\n\n2. **City Cell**:\n   - Location: 1st floor, P431, CIT Scheme VI-M, Kankurgachi, Kolkata\n   - Specializes in mobile repairs, including screen replacements.\n\n3. **Mobile World**:\n   - Location: 35/B, Canal Circular Rd, Kadapara, Phool Bagan, Kolkata\n   - Provides professional services for various smartphone brands.\n\n4. **Fixxo**:\n   - Location: Urban Sabujayan Complex, 16A-L2/0138 E M Bypass, Mukundapur, Kolkata\n   - Known for quick and reliable services with genuine parts.\n\n5. **New Market Mobile Repair**:\n   - Location: Near New Market area, Kolkata\n   - Offers a wide range of repair services, including screen replacements at competitive prices.\n\n6. **Reliance Digital**:\n   - Multiple locations across Kolkata including South City Mall and Quest Mall.\n   - Offers quality repair services with original parts and warranty.\n\n7. **Authorized Service Centers**:\n   - If you are looking for brand-specific repair, visiting an authorized service center for your phone brand (Apple, Samsung, MI, etc.) ensures original parts and reliable service.\n\nIt's recommended to call ahead to confirm the availability of parts, prices, and the estimated repair time. Reading online reviews and seeking recommendations from friends or family can also help in choosing a trustworthy repair shop.",
